+## Overview
+Total revenue reached $7,154.44 across 30 orders, covering four regions and four products. The median order value was $204.94, while the average order value was $238.48, so a few large orders raise the mean.
+
+## Top Products
+Gadget led with $2,392.00 from 7 orders, followed by Widget at $2,118.94, Doohickey at $1,513.00, and Sprocket at $1,130.50.
+
+## Regional Performance
+North led with $2,176.35, ahead of East at $1,830.79, South at $1,732.48, and West at $1,414.82. North and South each had 8 orders; East and West had 7.
+
+## Recommendations
+- Push Gadget, the top product at $2,392.00 over 7 orders, since its high price drives the most revenue.
+- Grow West, the lowest region at $1,414.82, toward North's $2,176.35 with targeted promotions.
+- Bundle Sprocket, the weakest line at $1,130.50, with Widget to raise its low order values.
